{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"10c3c91d58","title":"整风而外，可以考虑的几点建议","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3986598391","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"10c3c91d58"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"1b6d6991fb","name":"叶于泩"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"427b2cddd3","type":"title","text":"整风而外，可以考虑的几点建议","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"69b87a362c","type":"authors","text":"北京大学叶于泩","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"92d67caf7a","type":"subtitle","text":"（叶于泩：北京大学哲学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"ff93e13f19","type":"paragraph","text":"宪法规定的言论、出版、集会、结社的自由完全实现了吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"9394565814","type":"paragraph","text":"宪法规定的人民的选举权真正实现了吗？今后三害俱全的干部会不会仍旧有稳坐“钩鱼台”的可能？如果宪法规定的不可以实现，那么什么法制不可以违犯？如果法律、制度没有实现的可靠保证，那末要它何用？如果群众不能对领导实行严格的监督，那么领导的正确性又用什么来保证。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"a62f702750","type":"paragraph","text":"一切的最终保证在于实行彻底的社会主义民主。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"3c91997e65","type":"paragraph","text":"1．允许私人办报刊、出版社，取消出版的检查制度，开放禁书。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"c8aaf2a945","type":"paragraph","text":"2．实现集会、结社自由。让现存的各民主党派与共产党有同等的活动机会，同等的竞赛机会。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"df472db66f","type":"paragraph","text":"3．改造人民代表大会，让拥护公有制的各种意见在会上充分争鸣；国家大事的决定，要在公开讨论中形成。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"2f9a7dcf02","type":"paragraph","text":"4．严格的、具体的规定共产党在政权机关中的地位作用。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"},{"id":"04387472b8","type":"paragraph","text":"5．改进选举制度、让选举人自己提名、推荐，候选人名额应超过应选名额，让选举人有选举的余地。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58"}],"page":{"id":"1d50158a6f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"10c3c91d58","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}